2015-01-15  Tomas Flouri  <Tomas.Flouri@h-its.org>
    * Release 0.9.6
    * Added zlib support
    * Fixed options:
      --left-fastq -> --forward-fastq
      --right-fastq -> --reverse-fastq
    * Added --nbase option that places an N as the result of merging when the
      base-pair to be merged consists of two different, non degenerate bases
    * Updated man-pages with new options

